blueprint.description:
12K a minute 12 beaconed Agricultural Science. 
Tileable in 1 direction
Yumako/Jellynut/Water inputs on each end
If it runs flat out with no stoppages no eggs hatch
I'd put laser turrets in as you're 100% going to backup at some point.

Havent taken into account seed usage but i use 4 heating towers to remove excess spoilage/seeds. 

Requires 157 Yumako/sec
Requires 55 JellyNut/sec
3450 Water/sec
No other inputs required besides the initial kickstart eggs/nutrients.
No Quality all Common
blueprint.label: Beaconed Agricultural Science 12k/m
